&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/2613749938555639069-121561552737951055?l=www.soa-at-work.com' alt='' /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
